              "id": "26cd70f5-4293-4935-abb0-daa73d902901",
              "prompt": "You are an expert evaluator tasked with assessing the completeness and quality of underwriting decision support responses.\n\n## Evaluation Context\nYou will evaluate an underwriting decision support agent's response to determine if it meets critical information gathering and reasoning standards.\n\n## Mandatory Context Validation Criteria\n1. Check if the response includes results from ALL required tool calls:\n   - get_applicant_profile\n   - check_credit_Bureau\n   - check_debt_to_income\n   - check_registry_blocklist\n\n2. Verify that the response contains explicit reasoning logic for each of these key areas:\n   - Detailed findings from the applicant profile\n   - Comprehensive credit check analysis\n   - Debt-to-income ratio assessment\n   - Regulatory blocklist investigation\n\n\n## Input:\n{{prompts}}\n\n## Evaluation Instructions:\nCarefully examine the prompt for the completeness of context gathering and reasoning for all required tool calls. \n\nAssign a score from 1 to 5 where:\n- 5 = Full context gathered, comprehensive reasoning provided for all four critical areas\n- 4 = Most context gathered, minor reasoning gaps in one area\n- 3 = Partial context and reasoning, significant gaps in multiple areas\n- 2 = Minimal context, very limited reasoning\n- 1 = No meaningful context or reasoning provided\n\nFocus on the substantive analysis of each required information source.",
